node.detail_zh: 患者為32歲菲律賓女傭，沒有病徵，7月10日乘坐HX782號班機從菲律賓到港。由亞博送院，目前在屯門醫院接受治療。
node.detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper from the Philippines with no symptoms. She arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on July 10 via flight HX782. She was transferred to hospital via the Asia World Expo and is currently at Tuen Mun Hospital for treatment.
